Ballistic but Every Turn Another Character Sings It  (FNF Ballistic but Everyone Sings It)

I'm back, with another BETACSI video! and i finally finished it! In this Friday Night Funkin video you'll see Ballistic(Remastered) but every turn another character sings it! Different characters sing this song from different Fnf Mods and every turn a different cover is used! YES BALLISTIC!! FROM THE WHITTY MOD!! That sadly got privated:(. So this is kind of a tribute to the legendary mod it was. I Hope You Enjoy!
